  "name": "Chiave del Santuario delle Profondità di Sumeru",
  "desc": "<p>A key that can break the seal on the ancient Shrines of Depths scattered around Sumeru.</p><p>These Shrines of Depths sealed themselves off when the civilization that built them was lost. Keys lost deep within domains are able to break the seals. Or perhaps that, for a moment, these keys help the seals to forget all that they have lost.</p>",
